OL,1,R+%|l4|,$|,$s  n=j=|h<| k4|l4|l4W?4   
OL,2,Rr5z5s{5s{5  j5j5jws z%z5z5Wu#m'm
OL,3,ECANINE RUMOUR MILLG``````````R,.%Wz'#p"
OL,4,B                               W zk  "u
OL,5,B"3Dfx is no longer involved in Wh!( `|
OL,6,Bthe development of Sega's      Wz~}|3
OL,7,Bfollow-up to the Saturn. I knowWu ba
OL,8,Bthis because it's true.        Woqs/a>
OL,10,F"The PC hardware company had been      
OL,11,Fworking on a graphics sub-system for   
OL,12,Fthe 64-bit Project Black Belt.         
OL,13,B                                       
OL,14,B"Independent statements issued by Sega 
OL,15,Band 3Dfx late last week confirmed      
OL,16,Brumours that the two firms had broken  
OL,17,Boff their potentially lucrative        
OL,18,Bpartnership. No reasons were given."   
OL,20, ``````````````````````````````````1/5``
OL,21,B       LettersF174  BReviewsF172       
OL,22,C]D  BLOCKBUSTER PLAYSTATION UK GAMES   
OL,23,C]DTOURNAMENT - p622 C4 FOR INFORMATION 
OL,24,AReviews   BReviews   CGreen   FTV      
PN,17102
SC,0002
FL,172,173,160,110,1ff,170
OL,1,R+%|l4|,$|,$s  n=j=|h<| k4|l4|l4W?4   
OL,2,Rr5z5s{5s{5  j5j5jws z%z5z5Wu#m'm
OL,3,ECANINE RUMOUR MILLG``````````R,.%Wz'#p"
OL,4,B                               W zk  "u
OL,5,B"Insiders report that Sega's   Wh!( `|
OL,6,Bdecision to break off its      Wz~}|3
OL,7,Bpartnership with 3Dfx was not  Wu ba
OL,8,Bdown to either performance or  Woqs/a>
OL,9,Bcost issues regarding the 3D chip.     
OL,11,F"3Dfx has been left baffled by the     
OL,12,Fsudden axing of its contract. Sega is  
OL,13,Fnow believed to be in negotiations with
OL,14,Fa number of other 3D graphics hardware 
OL,15,Fspecialists.                           
OL,17,B"Power VR is the front runner to pick  
OL,18,Bup where 3Dfx left off."               
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````2/5``
OL,21, BTeen for twoF140BObserve the indexF170
OL,22,B]MD BAMBER IN DARK AVENGER PROBE p152  
OL,24,AReviews   BReviews   CGreen   FTV      
PN,17103
SC,0003
FL,172,173,160,110,1ff,170
OL,1,R+%|l4|,$|,$s  n=j=|h<| k4|l4|l4W?4   
OL,2,Rr5z5s{5s{5  j5j5jws z%z5z5Wu#m'm
OL,3,ECANINE RUMOUR MILLG``````````R,.%Wz'#p"
OL,4,B                               W zk  "u
OL,5,B"3Dfx is known to be evaluatingWh!( `|
OL,6,Bits legal options in the wake  Wz~}|3
OL,7,Bof its contract break-up with  Wu ba
OL,8,BThe Mighty Seed (Sega)."       Woqs/a>
OL,10,F"Sega, a major shareholder in 3Dfx -   
OL,11,Fmaking the situation even more bizarre 
OL,12,F- will do what it can to ensure the    
OL,13,Fmatter does not end up in court.       
OL,15,B"Despite all this, Sega has still yet  
OL,16,Bto officially confirm the existence of 
OL,17,BProject Black Belt - despite statements
OL,18,Bby its CEO and others."                
OL,20, ``````````````````````````````````3/5``
OL,21,B       LettersF174  BReviewsF172       
OL,22,B]MD      TURNER THE WIG p196           
