OL,1,R+%|l4|,$|,$s  n=j=|h<| k4|l4|l4W?4   
OL,2,Rr5z5s{5s{5  j5j5jws z%z5z5Wu#m'm
OL,3,ECANINE RUMOUR MILLG``````````R,.%Wz'#p"
OL,4,B                               W zk  "u
OL,5,B"Unlike the Saturn version,    Wh!( `|
OL,6,BDuke Nukem on the Nintendo 64  Wz~}|3
OL,7,Bwon't be released without a    Wu ba
OL,8,Blittle tampering from Doctor   Woqs/a>
OL,9,BCensorship, I hear.                    
OL,11,F"The strippers seen in early levels of 
OL,12,Fthe game have been covered up with T-  
OL,13,Fshirts. Also, you'll be unable to shoot
OL,14,Fthem as before - instead you'll be     
OL,15,Fgiven a new objective to save them from
OL,16,Fthe pig-faced aliens.                  
OL,18,B"But listen - there's a four-player    
OL,19,Bmode, plus new weapons and levels too."
